ver-who-ran-over-protesters-to-stay-in-custody-as-police-appeal-accepted/0000018e-c3c2-dc93-adce-eff23a150000</guid></item><item><title>“我来自美国，婊子”：美国直播主播约翰尼·索马里因涉嫌骚扰女警察而在以色列被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-livestreamer-johnny-somali-arrested-in-israel-on-suspicion-of-harassing-policewoman/0000018e-c380-dc93-adce-eff0f9720000</link><description>约翰尼·索马里在特拉维夫的一次抗议活动中被捕并被释放，随后因警方发现一段他对女警察使用粗俗语言的在线视频而再次被捕。索马里称自己被捕是“假新闻”，他面临听证会，可能会被驱逐出境</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 17:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-livestreamer-johnny-somali-arrested-in-israel-on-suspicion-of-harassing-policewoman/0000018e-c380-dc93-adce-eff0f9720000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官称，以色列公司 Cognyte 在未经许可的情况下向缅甸出售网络情报系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-company-cognyte-sold-spyware-to-myanmar-without-license-says-state-attorney/0000018e-c2fa-dc93-adce-eefaa19f0000</link><description>《国土报》透露，科格尼特向缅甸出售网络情报系统，违反了全球武器禁运，并且以色列宣布已停止向该国出口武器，但总检察长办公室宣布不会展开调查</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 16:47:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-company-cognyte-sold-spyware-to-myanmar-without-license-says-state-attorney/0000018e-c2fa-dc93-adce-eefaa19f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 186 天：哈马斯称新的停战提议无法满足其要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-186-hamas-says-new-truce-proposal-doesnt-meet-its-demands/0000018e-c391-d480-a99e-cfd7c5bf0001</link><description>哈马斯表示，最近的人质释放/停火提议未能满足巴勒斯坦各派别的要求 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，伊朗正在通过中东向约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人走私武器 ■ 沃伦参议员成为第一位表示以色列在加沙的行动可能在法律上构成种族灭绝的美国参议员■ 土耳其将限制对以色列的各种出口，直至宣布加沙停火 ■ 战争开始 186 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 16:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-186-hamas-says-new-truce-proposal-doesnt-meet-its-demands/0000018e-c391-d480-a99e-cfd7c5bf0001</guid></item><item><title>民主党高层不会就即将向以色列出售 F-15 给予拜登橡皮图章，这可能会改变游戏规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</link><description>众议院外交事务委员会的首席民主党人宣布，他正在等待拜登就以色列在加沙的行为做出保证，然后才会批准向以色列出售价值 180 亿美元的 F-15 战斗机。他说：“我认为不分青红皂白的轰炸已经够了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</guid></item><item><title>“证据不足”：德国在国际法院否认协助以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</link><description>德国的一名法律顾问表示，尼加拉瓜在联合国最高法院的案件很仓促，应该被驳回，因为德国和其他西方国家面临着向以色列出口武器的抗议。德国是以色列最大的武器供应国之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</guid></item><item><title>德国公司以加沙战争为由拒绝向以色列残奥会提供门球供应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</link><description>德国公司 KSG GmbH 做出这一决定是因为它相信“采取这一立场对于坚持我们的原则和支持和平解决冲突的努力是必要的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，本-格维尔的警察局长任命将完成他对以色列警察的接管</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</link><description>“罪犯第一次任命专员”：以色列警方高层将本-格维尔对警察局长的选择描述为极右翼国家安全部长及其幕僚长（前山顶人物）的“傀儡”和“唯唯诺诺的人”青年活动家</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长决定独立日仪式在没有观众的情况下举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-decides-independence-day-ceremony-to-be-held-without-an-audience/0000018e-c2c1-d480-a99e-ced72cc20000</link><description>在决定仪式不包括烟花表演后，利库德集团部长米里·雷格夫现在表示，出于安全考虑，仪式将在没有观众的情况下举行，并提前拍摄。在 Ynet 新闻播出的一段录音中，在加沙被扣押的人质的母亲要求雷格夫取消仪式</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:47:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-decides-independence-day-ceremony-to-be-held-without-an-audience/0000018e-c2c1-d480-a99e-ced72cc20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列市长因伊朗袭击紧急准备而引起居民恐慌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-israeli-city-panics-residents-over-emergency-preparations-for-iranian-attack/0000018e-c28c-d877-a7be-f2ff6e170000</link><description>以色列南部城市阿什杜德上周在以色列杀害一名伊朗高级将军后发表声明，呼吁该市每户家庭“组织起来，做好应对与广泛导弹有关的紧急情况的准备”攻击&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/mayor-of-israeli-city-panics-residents-over-emergency-preparations-for-iranian-attack/0000018e-c28c-d877-a7be-f2ff6e170000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府正在用资金消除绿线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</link><description>预算逐个预算，法律逐个法律：从强迫手机公司扩大在被占领土的覆盖范围到促进公共资金向定居点转移的法律。这就是内塔尼亚胡的极右政府正在努力实现事实上的吞并</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:06:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-government-is-eliminating-the-green-line-with-money/0000018e-bcd4-d7ee-a39e-fdfebb870000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和以色列贸易针锋相对，关系进一步恶化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</link><description>土耳其已经停止向以色列发送任何可用于军事目的的货物。以色列表示将通过限制从土耳其进口的产品来回应这些措施</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-09/ty-article/turkey-slams-israel-with-export-sanctions-until-gaza-cease-fire-achieved/0000018e-c25b-d6f4-afaf-ee5b08c00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯赢了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</link><description>哈马斯颠覆了以色列在军事上所向披靡的剧本，暴露了其国际支持的脆弱性，引发了对其长期可持续性的严峻质疑。西方、温和的阿拉伯国家、以色列和巴勒斯坦权力机构有责任阻止他们取得任何最终胜利</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/has-hamas-won/0000018e-c21d-d1b7-a3af-e71f0f590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府报告显示，自 10 月 7 日和加沙战争以来，以色列收到的捐款已达 14 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</link><description>新报告显示，这 14 亿美元中约有一半是由北美犹太联合会及其 146 个成员组织筹集的，大约 58,000 名志愿者从国外飞往以色列</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/donations-to-israel-since-oct-7-and-gaza-war-top-1-4-billion-israeli-govt-report-finds/0000018e-c219-d480-a99e-ce5f096c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长因法律困难否决本格维尔的警察发言人候选人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</link><description>消息人士称，如果国家安全部长批准提拔本-格维尔在警察内部的同僚，以色列警察局长同意聘请本-格维尔的候选人担任警察发言人</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-vetoes-appointment-of-ben-gvirs-candidate-as-police-spokesperson/0000018e-c1b2-d6f4-afaf-edf2c6ca0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事演习缓解加沙压力，为人质谈判提供关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙南部撤军以及援助物资数量增加两倍可能有助于谈判，或者让辛瓦尔觉得不必着急，从而威胁到以色列脆弱的联盟。与此同时，哈马斯和巴勒斯坦权力机构为控制加沙剩余的民事机构进行了一场悄悄的战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-maneuvers-ease-pressure-on-gaza-presenting-key-moment-for-hostage-talks/0000018e-bf36-d92b-adaf-ff763abc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全内阁讨论加沙谈判；美国称哈马斯尚未对提议做出回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</link><description>《华尔街日报》：美国人质协议提案包括将15万巴勒斯坦人送回加沙北部 ■ 法国、埃及、约旦领导人呼吁加沙“立即停火” ■ 哈马斯称以色列提议未能满足巴勒斯坦人的要求，将继续审查 ■ 内塔尼亚胡表示拉法行动日期已定</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 02:27:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-live/naval-iron-dome-intercepts-target-over-red-sea-for-first-time-hamas-no-progress-on-talks/0000018e-c0a2-db65-a7af-d0aab8ef0000</guid></item><item><title>费城剧院因担心亲巴勒斯坦人的强烈反对而取消放映以色列电影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</link><description>布林莫尔电影学院原定在费城举行的年度以色列电影节上放映一部关于以色列音乐家耶胡达·波利克 (Yehuda Poliker) 的纪录片，但在提前一天通知后就取消了该学院</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/philadelphia-theater-nixes-screening-of-israeli-film-over-fear-of-pro-palestinian-backlash/0000018e-bfdc-db65-a7af-ffdcb9a70000</guid></item></channel></rss>